Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED01「Twinkle Starlight」----------
Comment: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,見上げた空高く
Comment: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,降り注ぐきらめきよ
Comment: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Brilliant，
Comment: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonder Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:07.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,このまま　そっと目蓋とじても
Comment: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:16.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,胸にきらり　輝くよ
Comment: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,たとえばそうこんな雨の日
Comment: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,雲間から覗く空に
Comment: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:32.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,明日ヘの願いを込めて
Comment: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:36.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,きっとそこにあるよ（Eternal Starlight）
Comment: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,導くひかりを（Beyond The Night）
Comment: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:44.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,追いかけ続ける（Over The Blue Sky）
Comment: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:50.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,幼い日のような澄んだ瞳で
Comment: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:51.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,だから
Comment: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,無窮にまたたく星よ
Comment: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:59.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,希望の祈りたちよ
Comment: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:06.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,想いのせ　銀河の果てまでも
Comment: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle Star.
Comment: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:14.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Shiny，Bright In The Sky.
Comment: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:21.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonderful Twinkle Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:52.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,抬頭仰望無垠夜空
Comment: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:55.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,無數星辰悄然灑落
Comment: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃爍之間
Comment: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,漫天璀璨
Comment: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:07.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使輕輕地閉上雙眼
Comment: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:16.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,無盡的光輝猶在心間
Comment: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:21.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使整天下雨淅淅瀝瀝
Comment: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也想透過雲隙仰望天際
Comment: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:32.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後許下明日的懇祈
Comment: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:36.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,它一定就在那{\fnFOT-Chiaro Std B}裡{\fn}（永恆星光）
Comment: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,那指引我的絢麗（劃過黑夜）
Comment: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:44.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會不住地尋覓（踏上碧空）
Comment: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:50.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為眼瞳依舊像兒時那般清晰
Comment: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:51.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以啊
Comment: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,無數閃爍的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:59.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,無數希望的祈願啊
Comment: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:06.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,帶著我的思念　飛向銀河的盡頭吧
Comment: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃爍明亮的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:14.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,放射光明在天際啊
Comment: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,哇~
Comment: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:21.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,閃爍星光灑滿天
